00046 /*
00047  * Open the files.
00048  */
00049 bool CHPCompareGCOStoCalvin::OpenFiles(const char *gcosFile, const char *calvinFile)
00050 {
00051         gcos.SetFileName(gcosFile);
00052         if (gcos.Read() == false)
00053         {
00054                 differences = "Failed to read the GCOS file\r\n";
00055                 return false;
00056         }
00057 
00058         CHPFileReader reader;
00059         try
00060         {
00061                 reader.SetFilename(calvinFile);
00062                 reader.Read(calvin);
00063         }
00064         catch (...)
00065         {
00066                 differences = "Failed to read the Calvin file\r\n";
00067                 return false;
00068         }
00069         return true;
00070 }

00125  * Compare the algorithm parameters.
00126  */
00127 void CHPCompareGCOStoCalvin::CompareAlgParams()
00128 {
00129         TagValuePairTypeList &gparams = gcos.GetHeader().AlgorithmParameters();
00130         ParameterNameValueTypeVector cparams = calvin.GetAlgParams();
00131         CHPCompareUtils::CompareInts((int)gparams.size(), (int)cparams.size(), differences, "algorithm parameters size");
00132         if (gparams.size() != cparams.size())
00133         {
00134                 return;
00135         }
00136         int index=0;
00137         for (TagValuePairTypeList::iterator it = gparams.begin(); it!=gparams.end(); ++it)
00138         {
00139                 TagValuePairType &gparam = *it;
00140                 ParameterNameValueType &cparam = cparams[index++];
00141                 CHPCompareUtils::CompareStrings(gparam.Tag, cparam.GetName(), differences, "algorithm parameter name");
00142                 CHPCompareUtils::CompareStrings(gparam.Value, cparam.ToString(), differences, "algorithm parameter value");
00143         }

00171 void CHPCompareGCOStoCalvin::CompareBackground()
00172 {
00173         BackgroundZoneTypeList &zones = gcos.GetHeader().GetBackgroundZones();
00174         CHPCompareUtils::CompareInts((int)zones.size(), calvin.GetBackgroundZoneCnt(), differences, "bg zone count");

00176         {

00182         for (BackgroundZoneTypeList::iterator it=zones.begin(); it!=zones.end(); ++it)

00186                 CHPCompareUtils::CompareFloats(gzone.background, czone.GetBackground(), differences, "background");
00187                 CHPCompareUtils::CompareFloats(czone.GetCenterX(), gzone.centerx, differences, "zone centerx");
00188                 CHPCompareUtils::CompareFloats(czone.GetCenterY(), gzone.centery, differences, "zone centery");

00192 /*
00193  * Compare the data
00194  */
00195 void CHPCompareGCOStoCalvin::CompareData()
00196 {
00197         if (gcos.GetHeader().GetAssayType() == CCHPFileHeader::Expression)
00198                 CompareExpression();
00199 
00200         else if (gcos.GetHeader().GetAssayType() == CCHPFileHeader::Genotyping)
00201                 CompareGenotyping();
00202 
00203         else if (gcos.GetHeader().GetAssayType() == CCHPFileHeader::Universal)
00204                 CompareUniversal();
00205 
00206         else if (gcos.GetHeader().GetAssayType() == CCHPFileHeader::Resequencing)
00207                 CompareResequencing();
00208 }

00210 /*
00211  * Compare the expression results
00212  */
00213 void CHPCompareGCOStoCalvin::CompareExpression()
00214 {
00215         int n=gcos.GetHeader().GetNumProbeSets();
00216         for (int i=0; i<n; i++)
00217         {
00218                 CHPExpressionEntry centry;
00219                 CExpressionProbeSetResults *gentry = gcos.GetExpressionResults(i);
00220                 calvin.GetEntry(i, centry);
00221                 CHPCompareUtils::CompareFloats(gentry->DetectionPValue, centry.GetDetectionPValue(), differences, "detection p-value");
00222                 CHPCompareUtils::CompareFloats(gentry->Signal, centry.GetSignal(), differences, "signal"); 
00223                 CHPCompareUtils::CompareInts(gentry->NumPairs, centry.GetNumPairs(), differences, "pairs");
00224                 CHPCompareUtils::CompareInts(gentry->NumUsedPairs, centry.GetNumPairsUsed(), differences, "pairs used");
00225                 CHPCompareUtils::CompareInts(gentry->Detection, centry.GetDetection(), differences, "detection");
00226                 CHPCompareUtils::CompareInts(gentry->m_HasCompResults, centry.GetHasComparisonData(), differences, "comp flag");
00227                 if (gentry->m_HasCompResults)
00228                 {
00229                         CHPCompareUtils::CompareFloats(gentry->ChangePValue, centry.GetChangePValue(), differences, "change p-value"); 
00230                         CHPCompareUtils::CompareFloats(gentry->SignalLogRatio, centry.GetSigLogRatio(), differences, "slr"); 
00231                         CHPCompareUtils::CompareFloats(gentry->SignalLogRatioLow, centry.GetSigLogRatioLo(), differences, "slr-low"); 
00232                         CHPCompareUtils::CompareFloats(gentry->SignalLogRatioHigh, centry.GetSigLogRatioHi(), differences, "slr-high"); 
00233                         CHPCompareUtils::CompareInts(gentry->NumCommonPairs, centry.GetCommonPairs(), differences, "common pairs");
00234                         CHPCompareUtils::CompareInts(gentry->Change, centry.GetChange(), differences, "change");
00235                 }
00236         }
00237 }

00276 /*
00277  * Compare resequencing results.
00278  */
00279 void CHPCompareGCOStoCalvin::CompareResequencing()
00280 {
00281         CResequencingResults *gresults = gcos.GetResequencingResults();
00282         CHPCompareUtils::CompareInts(gresults->GetCalledBasesSize(), calvin.GetEntryCount(), differences, "base count");
00283         if (gresults->GetCalledBasesSize() != calvin.GetEntryCount())
00284                 return;
00285 
00286         int n=gresults->GetCalledBasesSize();
00287         CHPReseqEntry ce;
00288         for (int i=0; i<n; i++)
00289         {
00290                 calvin.GetEntry(i, ce);
00291                 CHPCompareUtils::CompareInts(gresults->GetCalledBase(i), ce.call, differences, "base call");
00292                 CHPCompareUtils::CompareFloats(gresults->GetScore(i), ce.score, differences, "base score");
00293         }
00294 
00295         CHPCompareUtils::CompareInts(gresults->GetForceCallsSize(), calvin.GetForceCnt(), differences, "force size");
00296         if (gresults->GetForceCallsSize() != calvin.GetForceCnt())
00297                 return;
00298         n=gresults->GetForceCallsSize();
00299         ForceCallType gf;
00300         CHPReseqForceCall cf;
00301         for (int i=0; i<n; i++)
00302         {
00303                 gf = gresults->GetForceCall(i);
00304                 calvin.GetForceCall(i, cf);
00305                 CHPCompareUtils::CompareInts(gf.position, cf.position, differences, "force position");
00306                 CHPCompareUtils::CompareInts(gf.call, cf.call, differences, "force call");
00307                 CHPCompareUtils::CompareInts(gf.reason, cf.reason, differences, "force reason");
00308         }
00309 
00310         CHPCompareUtils::CompareInts(gresults->GetOrigCallsSize(), calvin.GetOrigCnt(), differences, "orig size");
00311         if (gresults->GetOrigCallsSize() != calvin.GetOrigCnt())
00312                 return;
00313         n=gresults->GetOrigCallsSize();
00314         BaseCallType go;
00315         CHPReseqOrigCall co;
00316         for (int i=0; i<n; i++)
00317         {
00318                 go = gresults->GetOrigCall(i);
00319                 calvin.GetOrigCall(i, co);
00320                 CHPCompareUtils::CompareInts(go.position, co.position, differences, "orig position");
00321                 CHPCompareUtils::CompareInts(go.call, co.call, differences, "orig call");
00322         }
00323 }
